{"tid":153491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國潮興吃特色菜「地雷」　重慶女不慎爆炸受傷","createTime":"2017-03-12T15:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T11:47:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29782a596690f43b3b8878e6eef435ee9b1bc44f","tid":153491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170312172805\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170312172805&h=fbbf0cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">陳女（箭嘴示）跟同學飯聚時，特色菜「地雷」發生爆炸，遭裝置碎片及熱湯燙傷。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n中國有一道名為「地雷」的特色菜，餸菜裝在一個酷似「地雷」的裝置內，食客進食前需點燃設在裝置的引線，裝置便會打開。重慶沙坪壩區一名陳姓女子昨日跟舊同學飯聚，也點了這道菜，沒料她在點燃「地雷」後，「地雷」果真「爆炸」，餸菜的熱湯及裝置碎片炸飛，致陳臉部燙傷。經協調後，餐廳老闆向陳女賠償500元（人民幣‧下同）作檢查治療費用。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚陳女跟高中同學到涉事餐廳飯聚，眾人經侍應推薦，點了特色菜「地雷」。上菜後，陳女等人按侍應指示，點燃「地雷裝置」的引線，未料裝置瞬間發生爆炸，裝置的碎片及餸菜燙熱的湯汁飛濺出來，致陳女臉部受傷，其羽絨被燒了幾個窟窿。<br />\n<br />\n意外後，陳女等人找餐廳老闆協商處理事件，惟溝通期間陳等人認為侍應態度不佳，於是報警求助。警方到場了解並查看陳女傷勢，發現其臉部傷勢並不算嚴重。經警方調解，餐廳老闆向陳女及其同學賠禮道歉，並支付陳女500元檢查治療費，雙方達成和解。<br />\n<br />\n另針對餐館在管理中存在的安全問題，警員亦當場提出整改建議，餐廳老闆亦答應立即進行整改，及對員工進行教育培訓。"},{"pid":"19e3ddc47dc772c6838276d06a7785770351464f","tid":153491,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"想知運作正常係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd4a882e0fec65dfe59f5e8e352ad9b8e194e97","tid":153491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170312172805\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170312172805&h=4f45f077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食客點燃「地雷」裝置的引線後，裝置便會炸開。（網上圖片"},{"pid":"0209ebe8db76c3fab8715cfac8c260c2cb3cdb06","tid":153491,"uid":26771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"中國製地雷竟然會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30873fb275b5e8cd655a1a039e9be5e057102e0f","tid":153491,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"邊個話中國炸彈唔會爆"},{"pid":"2eb762066b3a41f11ff2f37cde9f6993d90fce2d","tid":153491,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乞衣價"},{"pid":"5609b5ba3ed62e3f55d22de67e0decdac0429653","tid":153491,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"支那對爆炸依樣文化真係好博大精深"},{"pid":"1a6569c3fa8f96e9b6d272a913b026aeceb8e814","tid":153491,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04a2c22c7421159c24c9796751847555e7c164ad","tid":153491,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be66a6d7b13a9222095204f09ab8208fdae202a","tid":153491,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170312172805\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170312172805&h=4f45f077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食客點燃「地雷」裝置的引線後，裝置便會炸開。（網上圖片</blockquote><br />\n點睇都似炸彈多過地雷"},{"pid":"6b5c82dd4eaf46b778c2685322f17c2beaf5a241","t